[{"id":"FT1580","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p><span aria-label=\"An equation for f of x with two functions. The first function reads: f of x equals, c times x plus d, for x less than or equal to 2. The second function reads: f of x equals, x squared minus c times x, for x greater than 2.\"><math> <mrow> <mi>f</mi> <mtext> </mtext> <mrow> <mo>(</mo> <mi>x</mi> <mo>)</mo> </mrow> <mo>=</mo> <mrow> <mo>{</mo> <mtable columnalign=\"left\"> <mtr> <mtd> <mi>c</mi> <mi>x</mi> <mo>+</mo> <mi>d</mi> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext>&nbsp;for&nbsp;</mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mi>x</mi> <mo>≤</mo> <mn>2</mn> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <msup> <mi>x</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mo>−</mo> <mi>c</mi> <mi>x</mi> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext>&nbsp;for&nbsp;</mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mtext> </mtext> <mi>x</mi> <mo>&gt;</mo> <mn>2</mn> </mtd> </mtr> </mtable> </mrow> </mrow> </math></span></p>\n\n<p>Let <em>f</em> be the function defined above, where <em>c</em> and <em>d</em> are constants. If <em>f</em> is differentiable at <span aria-label=\"x is equal to 2 comma\"><math> <mrow> <mi>x</mi> <mo>=</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mo>,</mo> </mrow> </math></span> what is the value of <span aria-label=\"c plus d ?\"><math> <mrow> <mi>c</mi> <mo>+</mo> <mi>d</mi> <mo>?</mo> </mrow> </math></span></p>\n","choicesHtml":["<p>−4</p>","<p>−2</p>","<p>0</p>","<p>2</p>","<p>4</p>"],"answer":0}]